483
00:22:05,980 --> 00:22:07,060
I live here.

484
00:22:07,340 --> 00:22:09,140
I know all the families and their ancestors here.

485
00:22:09,420 --> 00:22:10,100
How about this?

486
00:22:10,400 --> 00:22:11,710
Have you heard of

487
00:22:11,860 --> 00:22:13,220
