546
00:24:01,920 --> 00:24:02,800
and came to mine for the rocks.

547
00:24:03,360 --> 00:24:05,510
They left holes all over the mountain.

548
00:24:06,380 --> 00:24:07,060
Five years ago,

549
00:24:07,290 --> 00:24:08,180
